    mechanism: "The process follows a four-step sequence: Listen fully without interrupting, Acknowledge the concern with genuine empathy, Respond with relevant evidence or reframing, and Confirm resolution by asking if the concern has been addressed. This creates a cycle of psychological safety that encourages further dialogue.",
